**Branch naming by stack** (`1 ticket = 1 branch = 1 PR` — see §12.1):
- **web / generic** → `feat/{{TRACKER_KEY}}-NNN-slug`, `fix/{{TRACKER_KEY}}-NNN-slug` — branched off
